Mod4 5 :MacroCmd {MoveTo 0 0 TopLeft} {ResizeTo 1366 768} {Raise}
Mod4 6 :MacroCmd {MoveTo 684 0 TopLeft} {ResizeTo 682 768} {Raise}
Mod4 7 :MacroCmd {MoveTo 0 385 TopLeft} {ResizeTo 682 383} {Raise}
